                  <h3>About ShowPlazza</h3>
                  <p>
                      <strong> ShowPlazza </strong> is Central India’s largest entertainment ticketing website.
                      Headquartered in Nagpur, it is the destination for movie and non-movie options like events,
                      plays and sports. With ticketing for over 100 screens across 11 Major cities in Central India,
                      Showplazza has partnerships with all Major & Minor Central India’s Multiplexes & Movie
                      Theaters.
                  </p>
                  <h3>Introduction</h3>
                  <p>
                      <strong> ShowPlazza </strong> is the one of the largest fast growing entertainment-ticketing portal in
                      Central India. As the premier ticketing source for all major events across 11 cities of Central
                      India, Showplazza’s website commonly experiences record traffic during blockbuster movie
                      releases or major Sporting & Cultural events.<br /><br />
                      The company’s current database infrastructure would be overwhelmed by the increased load,
                      resulting in poor performance, downtime, and a loss of ticket sales. To handle the onslaught of
                      traffic and keep pace with an overall increase in demand for its ticketing services, Showplazza
                      sought a solution that would scale the database infrastructure to keep up with customer
                      growth.
                  </p>
